io.parallec.core.actor.message

Class ResponseOnSingeRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.parallec.core.actor.message.ResponseOnSingeRequest

  • public class ResponseOnSingeRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    A single HTTP response for each http request Note that the failObtainResponse in the response is whether work successfully received. it is not about 200 code. The Single Response will be in error when the HTTP Worker fail to obtain the response back on condition of [CANCEL or PROCESS_ON_EXCEPTION or PROCESS_ON_TIMEOUT]
    Author:
    Yuanteng (Jeff) Pei
